* Description
This layer enables version-control friendly sentence-per-line support
for the LaTeX layer.
  - Visual line wrapping at WRAP-WIDTH characters
  - Automatic navigation via j|k and up|down accross visual lines
  - Automatic newlines after end-of-sentence characters
  - Unintrusive right-only fringe indicators

* Install
To use this configuration layer, add it to your =~/.spacemacs=. You will need to
add =version-control-lines= to the existing =dotspacemacs-configuration-layers=
list in this file.
